\par\plain {Evan hesitated, the warmth in his eyes now clouded by a flicker of doubt. "I think so?"}
\par\plain {"Feel this!" Laura pressed his hand harder against her ribs. "I don't think I've ever been this excited... or this terrified!"}
\par\plain {"Me neither," he admitted, his voice laced with a newfound tremor.}
\par\plain {He watched with a mixture of pride and apprehension as she subtly integrated the envelope into her stack. His voice dropped to a near whisper. "Remember, I updated the website last night. If she gets suspicious, that's our backup. And..." Evan paused, the weight of their fallback plan hanging in the air. "Let's hold off on the 'we'd do the same for each other' card unless it's the last resort, okay?"}
